Rajasthan
Nov 21, 2014
Rape
Description:
			A mutilated body of 35-years-old married woman was today recovered from roadside at Amet village, 30 kms from Rajsamand district.

The deceased was identified as Ladi Vaishnav, they said adding, her face was half burnt and the body was apparently hit by stones and thrown on the roadside.

Her husband was working in Mumbai, while she was living with her ten year old son in the village, they said.

The body has been sent for post mortem and further investigations are on, police said.

